{"tid":2470020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港電台千禧年代主持葉冠霖去咗邊？","createTime":"2021-03-31T15:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T14:19:07.000Z","uid":54187,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d260833cfaa3995a879bba0513c0a243243ce426","tid":2470020,"uid":54187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"聽佢訪問D 高官同議員聽得出佢D 邏輯思考好清晰，辯論能力好勁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多高官，湯渣同痰喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都俾佢問到口啞啞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好掛住佢做主持嘅感覺<br />\n上網睇淨係話佢主持千禧年代，但實情個節目已經轉咗蕭洛汶做主持，究竟佢去咗邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G7HNb1o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG7HNb1o.png&h=219f4bac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23f31cdc5fc4d5438e6be704563575094d2ddb4d","tid":2470020,"uid":54187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T23:51:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0308268dc93f56d531378f0b9ab58bbc837bb590","tid":2470020,"uid":71993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T23:57:27.000Z","msg":"升左？"},{"pid":"b5298d04ed379a53a914920d2b2d8e671db162b4","tid":2470020,"uid":54187,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0308268dc93f56d531378f0b9ab58bbc837bb590","tid":2470020,"uid":71993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T23:57:27.000Z","msg":"升左？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T00:53:55.000Z","msg":"之前見佢個title 都叫節目總監，唔知再上係咩，不過幾鍾意聽佢做節目"},{"pid":"9f3b2510fdd856f8878266fe7c60db0fa2b74aa8","tid":2470020,"uid":38456,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T00:59:58.000Z","msg":"好耐無聽到佢 佢先正 升左但無得聽佢把聲"},{"pid":"33